<br>
As I said it months ago and was ripped apart by fanboys, we now see a ton more people coming out of the wood work. <br>
<br>
By posting this I am hoping to accomplish 2 things. <br>
<br>
1&gt; Get people to quit paying for this half assed shit so the next company will release a decent game and not patch in the game at a later date. <br>
<br>
2&gt; If anyone thinks the game gets better when you level and RVR, think again. Save your money and your time now and do not even bother. In most cases you have to learn the hard way - either way if you are having fun thats your choice. But if you are expecting more...  You are going to be disapointed. <br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> Ok developers, I am 50, now what? <br>
<br>
Taking/defending keeps? This morning i died b/c pets were send on me through the keep doors and while on the ground within the keep I was DDed to death. Similarly, the enemy can target through doors on invaders! Line of sight bugs ruin it! <br>
<br>
Leveling lower characters? Aye, I do that a good bit - mezzing for lower groups is how i spend 1/3 of my time now. <br>
<br>
Kill NPC mobs? Serves no purpose. I do not need coin and I have all the armor that I need then some. There are no NPC mobs left to kill aside from the glacial giant. Total lack of extra high level mobs/areas and interesting, specialized loot. <br>
<br>
Skirmishing? Ok, do a lot of that. The back and forth pushing of the battle front between various gates and PK's gets old. Half of the time it is unbalanced in our favor or theirs such that it is no fun. The other half of the time it is all lagged up. <br>
<br>
Notice how sooo many lvl 48+'s are hardly playing at all? Most of the people that I know who made into their upper 40's are stopping due to issues in balancing and bugs. We get on for an hour or two, get frusterated, and log. <br>
<br>
This does not reflect the opinion of all high level characters, but it does many. I think that a lot of the archer classes are spared this grief, they have an interesting time sniping about. <br>
<br>
Please do something soon. <br>
<br>
Meranda Mist <br>
50 Sorceress <hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
